data.name: Mango and Black Bean Salsa with Tortilla Chips
data.quickTastyDescription: A refreshing and vibrant salsa that combines sweet mango with hearty black beans, served with crispy tortilla chips for the perfect snack or appetizer.
detailedCookingInstructions: In a mixing bowl, combine diced mango, black beans, red onion, and cilantro.
Add lime juice and salt to the mixture, stirring gently to combine all ingredients.
Taste and adjust seasoning if necessary.
Serve immediately with tortilla chips on the side.
